Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沃爾夫·安尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綽號白狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聯邦軍的王牌機師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就比試比試
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏的話 高達歸我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達 Genoace custom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與疑似UE的敵人遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴大家敵艦在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.69,0:00:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 沃爾夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也蠻能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始移居殖民衛星後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷經數百年宇宙時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪地球圈霸權的戰爭終於偃旗息鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的時代似乎降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和平卻如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的不明敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令一顆殖民衛星化作宇宙的塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這將成為百年漫長戰爭的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久 就要到殖民衛星法丁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 資料有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民衛星 法丁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷史悠久 規模最大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商業農業樣樣繁榮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特也沒精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…最近累壞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手又癢癢了 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥這東西會上癮的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.93,0:03:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦體驗過那種興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的日常生活就會變得索然無味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…只是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聞出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 不想去和平的托爾迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想繼續戰鬥的男人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但UE如果不停止攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不打
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也在對我說要我用高達保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 說你不想去托爾迪亞沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 和我無關就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我關心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了 只有那台白色機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果去托爾迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西自然歸我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受和平去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達絕不會讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後咱們大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 菲利特是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須想辦法阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被監察局專門傳喚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道為什麼吧 古魯迪克中校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.24,0:05:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不明白你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少給我裝蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有司令部的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就私自擔任天神號艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自命令艦船出航
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明顯違反軍紀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵達法丁後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會第一時間拘留你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍事法庭伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼想說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼優秀的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有選擇手段的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天體儀發生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主、副、後備網絡 均無法連接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然無法連接天體儀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法與外界取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能逃離諾拉前系統就有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有多久抵達法丁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,60分鐘左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用近距離可視光線通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與法丁取得聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給出宇宙港的圖像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是殖民衛星法丁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到信號
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允許貴艦入港
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請遵從指示 採取入港航行狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是天神號 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按指示航道入港
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 不能只顧著高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得趕快整理行李
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是法丁嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 太棒了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空港就這麼豪華
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克 別那麼興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天不想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 真不給面子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 今天就我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點事 想一個人呆會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆算什麼意思啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克·艾諾亞中校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍監察局已經下令拘留你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦天神號 根據當地標準時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在殖民衛星法丁滯留六天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經被下令拘留了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查了你在法丁銀行的秘密賬戶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受違法收入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允許沒有入港許可的船隻通過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的所作所為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果被拘留
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些也會在軍事法庭上公之於眾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在 最起碼現在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事 只有你知我知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長…長官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克中校的拘捕任務…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的嫌疑已經洗清
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:09:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號 古魯迪克中校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都獲得在法丁的滯留許可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說結束就結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允許再追究這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是古魯迪克艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你會來 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想問您！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迄今為止 只是想著擊敗UE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有其他想法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須真正意義上變強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則沒法拯救大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 怎麼才能變強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 是我東張西望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏別動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話來我們船上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你包紮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫菲利特 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾·加勒特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我強行成為了這艘天神號的艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號要為我所用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想拋棄平民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只顧自己逃命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那樣的話 你們早已經死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得確實沒錯 古魯迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:12:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺騙大家的做法始終是不對的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉上的你 至少讓人感覺不會欺騙別人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你 就好像換了個人似的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在現在的你手下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓菲利特 繼續駕駛高達戰鬥的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在和UE的戰鬥中喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對UE出沒規律的分析結果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據分析
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE潛伏在一座被棄置的要塞裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在進行奇襲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果錯過良機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE一定會繼續擴大勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 本艦天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在法丁盡可能補充戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作氣對UE實施打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太蠻幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和UE的戰鬥 交給聯邦軍去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的聯邦軍爛到了根上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特不是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能駕駛高達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要高達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是自私 太自私了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道這是自私自利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝菲利特哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我送你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了的話 家人會擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 沒有爸爸和媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說我是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流在宇宙的客船上的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一倖存的嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾 德西爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾 幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥好遲鈍好遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼感覺？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像似曾…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船上也有機動戰士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是高達？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心別再受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是位可愛的小客人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 舉手投足跟你有那麼點像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？像我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和德西爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:16:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩台UE的機動戰士型入侵衛星內部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當地聯邦軍啟動防禦系統開始迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敵系統發現兩台疑似UE機體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎已經到了衛星外面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開高達去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾 回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特？是菲利特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊的高達沒有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉 沃爾夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰在駕駛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能光看著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野 Genoace出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到高達被搶走激動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃爾夫 Genoace custom出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾 又在玩捉迷藏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種姿態下打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管不知道是哪來的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠻有兩下子的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像知道下次攻擊從哪裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 當時也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺能預判敵人的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和接觸德西爾時的感覺一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發什麼呆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩膩了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是…什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望還能見面 菲利特哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到時候 哥哥還活著 的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自行動讓我們很困擾 德西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就被發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被認可成為EDEN住人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然和那樣的傢伙發生關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為會很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大失所望
